OL,3,CLasers 'powered by sunlight' could
OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,FLasers that harness bacteria's natural
OL,7,Fability to convert sunlight into
OL,8,Fenergy could power missions to Mars
OL,9,Fand provide a source of clean energy
OL,10,Fon Earth, scientists have announced.
OL,12,FThe technology is inspired by the way
OL,13,Fplants and bacteria convert light into
OL,14,Fchemical energy through a process
OL,15,Fcalled photosynthesis.
