OL,3,CLasers 'powered by sunlight' could
OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,FUnlike conventional semiconductor
OL,7,Fsolar panels, which convert sunlight
OL,8,Finto electricity, this process would
OL,9,Fnot rely on any electronic components.
OL,11,FThe project ` called APACE ` is first
OL,12,Flooking at developing the technology
OL,13,Funder laboratory conditions, before
OL,14,Ftesting and refining its suitability
OL,15,Ffor use in space.
