OL,3,CLasers 'powered by sunlight' could
OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,FIf it is successful, the researchers
OL,7,Fsay it could be used by global space
OL,8,Fagencies to power space exploration `
OL,9,Fincluding lunar bases or missions to
OL,10,FMars ` as well as providing a new way
OL,11,Fof transmitting clean, wireless energy
OL,12,Fon Earth.
OL,14,FThe technology is being developed by
OL,15,Fan international team that includes
OL,16,Fresearchers at Heriot-Watt University
OL,17,Fin Edinburgh.
