OL,3,CLasers 'powered by sunlight' could
OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,FProfessor Erik Gauger, from the
OL,7,FInstitute of Photonics and Quantum
OL,8,FSciences at Heriot-Watt, said the
OL,9,Ftechnology was potentially a
OL,10,F"breakthrough in space power".
OL,12,F"Sustainable generation of power in
OL,13,Fspace, without relying on perishable
OL,14,Fcomponents sent from Earth, represents
OL,15,Fa big challenge," he said.
OL,17,F"Yet, living organisms are experts at
OL,18,Fbeing self-sufficient and harnessing
OL,19,Fself-assembly.
