OL,3,CLasers 'powered by sunlight' could
OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,F"Our project not only takes biological
OL,7,Finspiration but goes one step beyond
OL,8,Fby piggybacking on functionality that
OL,9,Falready exists in the photosynthetic
OL,10,Fmachinery of bacteria to achieve a
OL,11,Fbreakthrough in space power.
OL,13,F"Our APACE project aims to create a
OL,14,Fnew type of laser powered by sunlight.
