OL,3,CLasers 'powered by sunlight' could
OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,F"Regular sunlight is usually too weak
OL,7,Fto power a laser directly, but these
OL,8,Fspecial bacteria are incredibly
OL,9,Fefficient at collecting and
OL,10,Fchannelling sunlight through their
OL,11,Fintricately designed light harvesting
OL,12,Fstructures, which can effectively
OL,13,Famplify the energy flux from sunlight
OL,14,Fto the reaction centre by several
OL,15,Forders of magnitude.
OL,17,F"Our project will make use of this
OL,18,Flevel of amplification to convert
OL,19,Fsunlight into a laser beam without
OL,20,Frelying on electrical components.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
