OL,3,CLasers 'powered by sunlight' could
OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,F"We already know it is possible to
OL,7,Fgrow bacteria in space, for example
OL,8,Fthrough studies on the International
OL,9,FSpace Station. Some tough bacteria
OL,10,Fhave even survived exposure to open
OL,11,Fspace.
OL,13,F"If our new technology can be built
OL,14,Fand used on space stations, it could
OL,15,Fhelp to generate power locally and
OL,16,Feven offer a route to sending power to
OL,17,Fsatellites or back to Earth using
OL,18,Finfrared laser beams.
