OL,3,CLasers 'powered by sunlight' could
OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,F"This technology has the potential to
OL,7,Frevolutionise how we power space
OL,8,Foperations, making exploration more
OL,9,Fsustainable while also advancing clean
OL,10,Fenergy technology here on Earth.
OL,12,F"All major space agencies have lunar
OL,13,For Mars missions in their plans, and
OL,14,Fwe hope to help power them."
OL,16,FThe research team will begin by
OL,17,Fextracting and studying the natural
OL,18,Flight-harvesting machinery from types
OL,19,Fof bacteria that have evolved to
OL,20,Fsurvive in extremely low light
OL,21,Fconditions.
