OL,3,CLasers 'powered by sunlight' could
OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,FThese bacteria have highly specialised
OL,7,Fmolecular antenna structures that can
OL,8,Fcapture and channel almost every
OL,9,Fphoton of light they receive ` making
OL,10,Fthem nature's most efficient solar
OL,11,Fcollectors.
OL,13,FThe researchers will also develop
OL,14,Fartificial versions of these
OL,15,Fstructures and new laser materials
OL,16,Fthat can work with both natural and
OL,17,Fartificial light-harvesters.
