OL,4,Ctransform space travel, scientists say
OL,6,FThe researchers then plan to combine
OL,7,Fthese components into a new type of
OL,8,Flaser material and test it in
OL,9,Fincreasingly larger systems.
OL,11,FThe first prototype of the new
OL,12,Ftechnology is expected to be ready for
OL,13,Ftesting within three years.
OL,15,FThe four million euro (#3.34 million)
OL,16,FAPACE project is jointly funded by the
OL,17,FEuropean Innovation Council and
OL,18,FInnovate UK, part of UK Research and
OL,19,FInnovation.
